        "created_at": "2016-08-01T22:01:00.295+08:00",
        "updated_at": "2016-08-02T00:10:29.905+08:00",
        "title_en": "Introduction",
        "title_zh_cn": "公司概况",
        "title_zh_tw": "公司概況",
        "body_en": "\u003cp\u003eGCL New Energy is a world leader of new energy specialized in solar power generation, the world\u0026#39;s most professional company of solar power plant operation and maintenance, and an international company with energy storage technology, micro-grid and intelligent integration capabilities. Adhering to the strategy of \u0026ldquo;seeking collaborative innovation and development driven by technology and talents based on a combination between industry and finance\u0026rdquo;, we provide clean, safe and efficient energy for the society with a strategic positioning of both centralized and distributed solar projects development.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abo01.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abo02.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abo03.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abo04.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticodeng.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abo05.png\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eGCL New Energy Holdings Limited went public on Hong Kong Exchanges Limited in May 2014. GCL New Energy has rapidly built PV power plants throughout the world. It has established 26 power plants in 10 provinces and cities in China, with a total capacity exceeding 1000MW; The company\u0026#39;s targe for annual additional grid-connected capacity in 2015, 2016 and 2017 are 2000MW, 2500MW and 3000MW, respectively.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" height=\"301\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/aboutimgen.jpg\" width=\"733\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n",
        "body_zh_cn": "\u003cp\u003e协鑫新能源（HK0451）是全球领先的以太阳能发电为主的，集开发、建设、运营一体化的新能源企业。协鑫新能源拥有世界一流的科技研发团队和管理运营团队，在太阳能光伏电站项目的开发、建设、运营、维护、投融资及创新管理方面拥有丰富的经验。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e公司秉承产融结合、科技引领、人才汇聚、协同创新的战略思想，以集中和分布式并重发展的战略定位，持续为社会提供清洁、安全、高效、可持续发展的绿色能源。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ico_about01.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ico_about02.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ico_about03.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ico_about04.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticodeng.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ico_about05.png\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e协鑫新能源于2014年5月在香港联交所上市（0451.HK）,获得了资本市场的高度认可, 入选MSCI指数，并在上市一年内，荣获国内外多项大奖。当年最高市值接近200亿港币，上市半年内融资23.7亿港元。与保险公司签订了国内第一单太阳能光伏电站发电量损失综合运营保险。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/a.jpg\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n",
        "body_zh_tw": "\u003cp\u003e協鑫新能源是全球領先的專注從事太陽能發電的專業公司和太陽能電站運維商，是具備儲能技術、微電網及智慧一體化集成能力的國際化公司。公司秉承產融結合、科技引領、人才彙聚、協同創新的戰略思想，以集中和分散式並重發展的戰略定位，持續為社會提供清潔、安全、高效、可持續發展的綠色能源。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ab01.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ab02.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ab03.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticojia.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ab04.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/abouticodeng.png\" /\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/ab05.png\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e協鑫新能源於2014年5月在香港聯交所上市,獲得了資本市場的高度認可, 入選MSCI指數，並在上市一年內，榮獲國內外多項大獎。當年最高市值接近200億港幣，上市半年內融資23.7億港元。同時，協鑫新能源也是第一家獲得根據專案本身償債能力，無需擔保，可迴圈利用的境外建設期貸款的光伏上市公司，並與保險公司簽訂了國內第一單太陽能光伏電站發電量損失綜合運營保險。公司發展快速，截止2014年末，開工在建項目超過1000兆瓦，建成並網超過600兆瓦。公司2015年目標新增並網量為2GW，2016及2017年目標新增並網量為2.5GW和3GW。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/aboutimg.jpg\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n",
        "url": "about",
        "slug": "about"
    },
